data.description: Come see this completely remodeled and updated 3 bedroom home in Girard that includes a massive garage! 1 year home warranty offered for even more piece of mind. This home is move in ready with updates throughout the entire home. Kitchen has newer appliances, farm sink, finished butcher block counters, stunning custom kitchen island, beautiful tile floor in the kitchen/dining area. The living room hardwood floors are freshly stained and finished and look amazing, the original trim/woodwork has been left untouched to really bring out the classic woodwork this updated home offers. A fully updated half bathroom is on the main floor, with another updated full bathroom upstairs that includes whirlpool tub and 5 shower heads, with Jack and Jill sinks. Upstairs you'll find 3 bedrooms with beautiful original hardwood floors that have been freshly stained and finished. Covered front porch, fenced in backyard, all vinyl siding, 3 year old hot water tank, all cooper pipes in basement replaced. Downstairs is a nice dry basement that has another full bathroom. Home has 200 amp fuse panel.  Garage is 3-4 cars with its own fuse panel, 2 220 hook ups, ac and heat.
